[h4 id=BossMummies 
	" Boss: Mummies
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"I need to jump over the right mummy to get into a position where my holy water can reach it.
	$LF
	"The holy water does the same damage as your primary weapon, so I needed to pick up the chain whip earlier in the level.
	$LF
	"It however deals damage much faster than any of your other attacks.
	$LF
	"There is a new glitch here involving the holy water: it turns out that pausing can affect the damage cycle of the holy water, which allows it to do more damage per jug.
	$LF
	"Sometimes you can also whip through the damage of the holy water, sometimes your whip damage is simply ignored, which pausing can also affect.
	$LF
	"Pausing at the wrong time will reduce the damage of your holy water instead.
	$LF
	"I haven't quite figured out why exactly this happens, so the pausing that you see in the TAS was done by trial and error.
	$LF
	"This allowed to me to finish the fight with just one single holy water along with some judicious whipping, which is not only faster, but also convenient, since it saves a big heart that I don't need to pick up later.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Taking less damage in this level also means I lose less time to the health recharge after the level.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"All in all, Level 3 is done 39 frames faster than before.
	$LF
