	"I avoid damage from the final fleaman on this level, which saves 2 frames.
	$LF
	"This was already present in the previous TAS, however, it turns out that this only works some of the time.
	$LF
	"The reason for this is that the fleaman will only become active a random amount of time after the screen loads, which is determined by RNG when you enter the screen.
	$LF
	"Depending on when he activates, some of his jumping patterns can simply be impossible to get past.
